Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:05.92,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què?! Que has quedat amb algú, ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:09.32,White,,0,0,0,,Però que saps l'hora que és?Sí, sí, ho sé perfectament.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.24,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Com que ens has dit que vinguéssim a aquesta hora,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.96,Cyan,,0,0,0,,m'he pensat que era perquè volies que sortíssim a sopar juntes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.60,Cyan,,0,0,0,,El pare m'ha dit que sortia a emborratxar-se
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.20,White,,0,0,0,,amb l'amo del Cafè Poirot i amb tota la colla.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.28,0:00:22.28,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, ja el coneixes, el teu pare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.20,White,,0,0,0,,T'he fet venir perquè vull que coneguis una persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:26.16,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.80,White,,0,0,0,,(Mouri) Au, doncs, és hora de plegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:31.56,White,,0,0,0,,(telèfon)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.96,White,,0,0,0,,-(fax: xiulet)-Un fax, ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:39.76,White,,0,0,0,,Què deu haver passat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:42.20,White,,0,0,0,,(fax: xiulet)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.00,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! No pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:48.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Sinichi) "Una crisi que no sembla que tingui sortida."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un retorn inesperat que ho desencallarà tot."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:53.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Una batalla a tres bandes entre una campiona de judo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:54.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,en Kogoro i l'Eri."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult, i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:04.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Zettai zetsumei kanjou no arashi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:08.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,totsuzen araware juwaki wo nigiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:12.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Don't stop reisei ni negatteru koto na no?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:17.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Say good bye omowazu tsugete shimai sou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:23.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nukedasa na kereba ushinai takunai my on mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:26.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Konna ni mo aishite iru no ni!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:31.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,Subete ga riezon mune no oku de I need you baby sakenderu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:36.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Every night gimon ga semeteiru kedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:40.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Chanto kikoeru Love forever and only one.
