Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:58.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tobidasa na kereba ushinai takunai my on mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:03.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Konna ni mo aishite iru no ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:08.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Doko ka faraway Do you mind if I open the door? Sakenderu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:12.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Every night fuan to tatakau kokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:16.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Chanto kikoeru Love forever and only one.
